    <title>Framework &amp; Case Studies for Delivering a Successful Drupal Migration </title>
    <link>/drupal-govcon-2016/drupal-govcon-2016/sessions/framework-case-studies-delivering-successful-drupal-migration</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;This session will walk participants through how to deliver a successful Drupal migration. We will present a detailed software implementation framework that can be applied to any Drupal migration (or any software or data migration for that matter).  We will demonstrate the application of the framework to a Wordpress to Drupal migration case study and a Drupal to Drupal migration case study.  We will then use the framework to walk through a hypothetical Drupal 6/7 to Drupal 8 migration.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;dagny&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item odd&quot;&gt;carson&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-og-vocabulary field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Track:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session Tracks (Drupal GovCon 2016)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/session-tracks-drupal-govcon-2016/business-and-strategy&quot;&gt;Business and Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
     <pubDate>Fri, 20 May 2016 17:40:05 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>dagny</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">4296 at http://local.capitalcamp.com</guid>
