    <title>Working with nodes in bulk</title>
    <link>/drupal-govcon-2016/drupal-govcon-2016/sessions/working-nodes-bulk</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt; Views Bulk Operations (VBO) is a great module for performing operations on groups of nodes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will learn:&lt;/strong&gt; In this session you will learn how to create custom dashboards using views as well as configuring VBO.  Using VBO we will show how to update the content of many nodes with a single action&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intended Audience: &lt;/strong&gt;This session will be useful for both beginning and intermediate audiences.  Basic knowledge of views will be helpful, but some intro for beginners will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;lucas&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item odd&quot;&gt;miles&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-session-timeslot field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Time Slot(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots clearfix&quot; class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots&quot;&gt;
